latestPosts.caption:
Story Time 🔔: About three years ago, out of the blue, I was scouted and cast for a campaign that changed my life. The campaign, a launch campaign for @lovechildbymasaba , was my first tryst with modelling. Prior to this, the thought had never occurred to me and the suggestion was laughable.
Being a part of this campaign for @houseofmasaba in some way feels like a full circle moment, and I couldn’t be more grateful to everyone now and then who decided to give me a shot 🥹🥹🥹❤️❤️❤️❤️ @masabagupta @tarunvishwaofficial @vijendra.bhardwaj @khyatimashru @vanshvirmani @anumariyajose 
PS- Swipe to see me in all my red headed glory 💅
